WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Quetiles' is a game where your goal is to change all the tiles
so that they are all the same colour.

  It may sound simple, but there's a catch: because as you change
a tile, one or two other tiles will also change their colour.

  Each game board uses 5 different colours and these colours will
change following a certain order (for example: red-blue-green-
white-yellow-red...) but the tiles affected by the one you changed
will change their colour in the opposite order (yellow-white-
green-blue-red...).

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

  -Simple installation: just run the game and play!

  -You can choose between 4 game board sizes, from a 5 by 5 tiles
   board up to a 11 by 11 tiles board.

  -Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
   doesn't take ages to download :)

  -The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
   resizeable.

